sentence: In early trading on Monday, shares of UnitedHealth Group ( UNH ) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 3.8%.
Year to date, UnitedHealth Group registers a 21.2% gain.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Intel Corp ( INTC ), trading down 0.8%.
Intel Corp is lower by about 12.5% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are Procter & Gamble ( PG ), trading up 0.2%, and JPMorgan Chase ( JPM ), trading up 2.8% on the day.
